using pollscm: 
1) go to job configurations and go to triggers and select the poll scm 
2) add cron syntax e.g( * * * * *)

observations:-
1) jenkins talks to github (is new commit is done based on our time settings)
2) check timezones in ec2 instance and jenkins setting-> appearance->timezone
3) if new commits found then only pipeline triggers

using build periodically:-
1) go to job configurations and go to triggers and select build periodically
2) add cron syntax e.g( * * * * *)

observations:- 
1) irrespective of newer commits it will build on given time while configuring



